%%s','Featured Images'=>'Valitud pildid','Full Width Template'=>'Täislaiusega mall','Post Formats'=>'Postituse vormingud','Featured Image Header'=>'Valitud päisepilt','It looks like you\'re using an old version of %s. For the best WordPress experience, please update your browser.'=>'Näib, et kasutatav %s on vananenud. Parima kogemuse saamiseks soovitame seda uuendada.','It looks like you\'re using an insecure version of %s. Using an outdated browser makes your computer unsafe. For the best WordPress experience, please update your browser.'=>'Näib, et %s on selles versioonis ebaturvaline. Vananenud veebilehitseja on arvestatav turvarisk, soovitame lehitsejat uuendada.','There are some invalid menu items. Please check or delete them.'=>'Mõned menüü elemendid on vigased. Palun kontrolli või kustuta nad.','term nameName'=>'Nimi','meta nameName'=>'Nimi','theme nameName'=>'Nimi','You can find additional themes for your site by using the Theme Browser/Installer on this screen, which will display themes from the <a href="%s">WordPress Theme Directory</a>. These themes are designed and developed by third parties, are available free of charge, and are compatible with the license WordPress uses.'=>'Täiendavaid teemasid võid leida Teemapaigaldaja abil, mis näitab <a href="%s">WordPressi teemakataloogi</a> sisu. Need teemad on pärit eri autoritelt ning on tasuta ja WordPressi omaga kokkusobiva litsentsiga.','The uploaded file exceeds the %s directive that was specified in the HTML form.'=>'Üleslaetava faili maht ületab HTML-vormis sätestatud %s -määranguga lubatu.','External Libraries'=>'Välisteegid','Available Tools'=>'Saadaolevad töövahendid','Network Setup'=>'Võrguparameetrid','Translate this to be the equivalent of English Translators in your language for the credits page Translators sectionTranslators'=>'Tõlkijad','Every plugin and theme in WordPress.org&#8217;s directory is 100%% GPL or a similarly free and compatible license, so you can feel safe finding <a href="%1$s